ISLAMABAD, Aug 03 (APP): Secretary of the Women’s Parliamentary Caucus (WPC), Dr. Shahida Rehmani, on Saturday congratulated Ghazala Gola on her election as Chairperson of the Women’s Parliamentary Caucus of the Balochistan Assembly.
“We are delighted to see Gola take on this leadership role, and we are confident that her expertise and dedication will further empower women in Balochistan,” Dr. Rehmani said and added, the Women’s Parliamentary Caucus looks forward to working closely with Ghazala Gola to advance gender equality and women’s representation in Pakistan.
